{"tid":1729451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嗰枝真係箭？","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T08:45:48.000Z","uid":149563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cfa197f48425b94543ac982ce30d8b0765d38e","tid":1729451,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友之前學過弩<br />\n而弩箭係比弓箭短，就好似下面啲圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BipS40U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBipS40U.jpg&h=ebf672d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNmBNee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNmBNee.jpg&h=b70e9446&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4EzyUg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4EzyUg.jpg&h=c5858dd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾個問題值得深究：<br />\n點樣可以用箭水平射到小腿？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到底個popo企係邊度中箭？</span></strong> 嗰枝真係箭？<br />\n會唔會其實係弩呢？<br />\n<br />\n而點解會覺得奇怪係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">弩係需要同popo攞牌，而係香港玩弩嘅人其實好少，同埋玩弩好貴</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oiHtDo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoiHtDo8.png&h=413b16b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/licensing/arms/tc/als_C-1043.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Flicensing%2Farms%2Ftc%2Fals_C-1043.pdf&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=75d88e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/licensing/arms/tc/als_C-1043.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83ipbKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83ipbKR.jpg&h=a28dd6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果popo計返個射程同角度，其實即時搵返個人出嚟唔難。而事後透過弩牌照搵返嗰個人更加唔難，如果popo一直都捉唔到人，咁就知係人定係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人見解，大家可唔可以幫手查一查呢？"},{"pid":"d5dd1faaa6f4d31e8ca6ac7593169c5dc114b275","tid":1729451,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67d8be09277f1054f3209fbafeb0f23f40680d4","tid":1729451,"uid":297949,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"剪左架，開始成支的"},{"pid":"db45c92b6e69b108d8b17267da4abe072349a0b1","tid":1729451,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"弩射既都係箭<br />\n弓射既又係箭<br />\n工具不同都係射箭"},{"pid":"621ffad90dcd31476f0237d6750760f910f15a3e","tid":1729451,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"剪短左"},{"pid":"1ef1982c46c6ebf2812923b158214abcdce8ba63","tid":1729451,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"下次千祈唔好得春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c85517a1236439ea075348c80f92c38131c5bd","tid":1729451,"uid":85390,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwCtDud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwCtDud.jpg&h=0894b631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇多啲source啦 成篇文打完懶分析咁又要比人笑返轉頭架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41afbda0833501b9bc11b82e563c134a74a4230","tid":1729451,"uid":295602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"箭黎, 一般運動用嗰啲<br />\n處理傷口嗰陣剪短左啫<br />\n<br />\n如果真係機械弩佢仲企到咩"},{"pid":"2ab54d4d11a531a679bd0f2d4171530ef995e53c","tid":1729451,"uid":85926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{